WEBVTT

00:00.835 --> 00:03.044
(SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING)

00:21.592 --> 00:23.592
(SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES)

00:37.212 --> 00:40.675
GIRL: "I, who live
in the shelter
of the Most High,

00:40.710 --> 00:43.744
"who abide
in the shadow
of the Almighty,

00:43.779 --> 00:45.284
"will say to the Lord..."

00:45.319 --> 00:47.319
(CONTINUES PRAYING INDISTINCTLY)

00:49.191 --> 00:51.191
(KNOCK ON DOOR)
WOMAN: Annie.

00:52.359 --> 00:54.128
Are you in there?

00:54.163 --> 00:56.493
(KNOCK ON DOOR)
Annie, honey,
can I come in?

00:56.528 --> 00:57.527
(DOORKNOB RATTLING)

00:59.564 --> 01:01.795
Sweetie?

01:01.830 --> 01:04.897
Annie, open the door,
please?
(KNOCKING HARDER)

01:04.932 --> 01:06.569
Annie, let me in.
(CONTINUES PRAYING)

01:08.177 --> 01:10.408
Open the door, Annie.
(ANN WHIMPERS)

01:10.443 --> 01:11.739
Annie.

01:11.774 --> 01:13.543
(ANGRILY)
Let me in, Annie!

01:13.578 --> 01:15.710
(BANGING ON DOOR)
Annie!

01:15.745 --> 01:18.581
(AGGRESSIVELY)
Let me in! Let me in!

01:18.616 --> 01:20.352
Annie,
let me in, Annie!

01:20.387 --> 01:22.651
Let me in!

01:22.686 --> 01:24.356
(DOOR CRASHES)
(ANN SCREAMS)

01:26.657 --> 01:29.394
WOMAN 2:<i> Your mother,</i>
<i> she was schizophrenic?</i>

01:32.498 --> 01:35.400
These sessions
are mandatory for
all staff, Sister Ann.

01:39.505 --> 01:41.736
My mother struggled
with depression.

01:42.673 --> 01:45.179
And, yes,

01:45.214 --> 01:47.544
she was eventually
diagnosed with
schizophrenia.

01:47.579 --> 01:50.184
But even as a child,
I knew it was...

01:52.287 --> 01:53.286
more.

01:54.553 --> 01:55.552
More?

01:57.886 --> 01:59.391
I didn't have
a name for it.

02:01.296 --> 02:03.494
Every night,
she would come
into my room...

02:06.367 --> 02:07.927
<i>Sometimes she was</i>
<i>my mother.</i>

02:09.469 --> 02:10.633
<i>Beautiful.</i>

02:11.801 --> 02:12.800
<i>Loving.</i>

02:14.804 --> 02:16.441
<i>And sometimes</i>
<i>she wasn't.</i>

02:16.476 --> 02:17.904
(HUMMING)

02:19.380 --> 02:21.281
<i>She'd comb my hair.</i>

02:21.316 --> 02:22.315
(SHUDDERING)

02:23.252 --> 02:25.252
<i>She'd hum that song.</i>

02:29.522 --> 02:31.522
(HUMMING CONTINUES)

02:38.993 --> 02:40.333
She'd hurt me.

02:41.666 --> 02:43.765
And then she'd hold me
and cry and say

02:43.800 --> 02:46.240
the voice inside her head
made her do it.

02:48.002 --> 02:50.409
I'm so sorry, Ann.

02:50.444 --> 02:52.543
Abuse at the hands of
someone you trust is...

02:52.578 --> 02:55.282
My mother was incapable
of hurting me,

02:55.317 --> 02:56.481
she loved me.

02:59.552 --> 03:01.585
It was the thing
inside her.

03:02.885 --> 03:04.456
She was possessed.

03:10.992 --> 03:12.992
(ETHEREAL MUSIC PLAYING)

03:37.458 --> 03:38.457
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

03:56.070 --> 03:58.510
(SIGHS)
Ah, look who it is.

03:58.545 --> 04:01.513
ANN: Morning, Steve.
STEVE: Good morning.
Thanks.

04:03.110 --> 04:04.318
(BELL TOLLING)

04:16.596 --> 04:18.398
FATHER QUINN:
You make a good point.

04:18.433 --> 04:21.896
But no, we are not
more sinful today than
we were in the past.

04:23.504 --> 04:24.932
The human heart
has never changed.

04:25.836 --> 04:26.934
Sister Ann.

04:29.840 --> 04:31.642
What has changed

04:31.677 --> 04:33.908
is that there are
more possessions
reported today

04:33.943 --> 04:37.846
than at any other time
in history.

04:37.881 --> 04:42.356
We are losing a war
that has been raging
for centuries.

04:42.391 --> 04:43.786
We must
hold the line,

04:43.821 --> 04:45.018
fight for every soul.

04:47.924 --> 04:49.957
DR. PETERS:<i> During</i>
<i> the Spanish Inquisition,</i>

04:49.992 --> 04:53.664
the Catholic Church
was responsible for
the torture and death

04:53.699 --> 04:57.899
of thousands
of so-called heretics.

04:57.934 --> 05:00.407
Many were simply
those suffering from

05:00.442 --> 05:05.005
psychotic, mood, neurotic
and personality disorders.

05:05.040 --> 05:07.678
The very structure
you're sitting in

05:07.713 --> 05:10.142
was built
in the late 18th century

05:10.177 --> 05:13.420
in response
to a rise in the occult.

05:13.455 --> 05:17.457
The clergy would drag
women suspected of
practicing dark arts

05:17.492 --> 05:22.792
down to
the baptismal well to
free them of evil spirits.

05:22.827 --> 05:26.961
Countless were drowned
in holy water

05:26.996 --> 05:28.864
till eventually,
the practice was stopped.

05:28.899 --> 05:30.998
ANN: Sorry, Doctor.

05:31.033 --> 05:36.168
Are you denying that
there are legitimate
cases of possession?

05:36.203 --> 05:40.139
I've been here
long enough
to have seen things

05:40.174 --> 05:42.515
that I can't
account for.

05:42.550 --> 05:46.145
But one thing I do know
is the mind is
incredibly powerful.

05:46.180 --> 05:49.016
And it loves
to play tricks on us.

05:49.051 --> 05:52.789
To distort
our reality.

05:52.824 --> 05:57.695
Now, thankfully,
the Church's approach has
evolved over the centuries.

05:57.730 --> 06:01.732
<i> And that's where</i>
<i> psychiatrists like myself</i>
<i> come in.</i>

06:01.767 --> 06:06.000
<i> The Vatican's new guidelines</i>
<i> require anyone</i>
<i> suspected of possession</i>

06:06.035 --> 06:10.708
<i> to undergo in-depth physical</i>
<i> and psychological evaluations</i>

06:10.743 --> 06:13.678
<i> before being approved</i>
<i> the Rite of Exorcism.</i>

06:16.980 --> 06:18.980
(DARK MUSIC PLAYING)

06:22.656 --> 06:23.655
(BABY CRYING OVER SPEAKER)

06:30.125 --> 06:32.466
(READER TRILLS)
(DOOR BEEPS)

06:35.999 --> 06:37.900
How are we doing
today, Clark?

06:40.135 --> 06:41.574
Anything we can
get you to eat?

06:43.776 --> 06:45.644
Let's give
this applesauce
a go, huh?

06:53.115 --> 06:54.114
Hey.

06:55.018 --> 06:56.523
There we go.

06:59.187 --> 07:00.186
(GULPS)

07:02.696 --> 07:05.158
Oh, you like
the applesauce.

07:05.193 --> 07:06.665
I'll have to
remember that.

07:12.266 --> 07:13.507
(READER TRILLS)

07:15.940 --> 07:17.203
DR. PETERS:
I've ordered
a full blood panel

07:17.238 --> 07:21.581
as I do with
all of our
new patients.

07:21.616 --> 07:24.848
She was brought in
for assessment
after having seizures,

07:24.883 --> 07:28.687
muscle spasms,
incontinence
and hypersalivation.

07:28.722 --> 07:30.854
Natalie's mother
believes that

07:30.889 --> 07:33.087
she is being possessed
by some sort of
evil entity.

07:33.122 --> 07:36.530
And I believe
that the test results
will prove otherwise.

07:36.565 --> 07:38.994
(WHISPERS) She's not
as scary as she looks.

07:40.228 --> 07:41.931
DR. PETERS:
She can hear you.

07:44.573 --> 07:45.572
Gentlemen,
shall we?

07:47.235 --> 07:49.037
PRIEST 1: Thank you.
PRIEST 2: Thanks, Sister.

07:51.272 --> 07:53.679
ANN: You didn't
eat much.
Mmm.

07:56.783 --> 07:58.079
I like your, uh...

07:59.687 --> 08:00.719
dog?

08:00.754 --> 08:02.248
It's a train.

08:02.283 --> 08:03.590
That has a tail.

08:04.318 --> 08:06.285
It's an abstract.

08:06.320 --> 08:08.925
(SMACKS LIPS)
Well, then,

08:08.960 --> 08:11.862
you're officially
a starving artist.

08:13.800 --> 08:15.932
I don't know
why they don't
give you dessert.

08:18.167 --> 08:19.606
Thanks.
(CHUCKLES)

08:20.774 --> 08:22.202
What is it?

08:22.237 --> 08:24.303
Oh, some sort of
nougaty goodness.

08:25.174 --> 08:26.712
What's nougat?

08:28.617 --> 08:30.650
I don't know.

08:30.685 --> 08:32.113
(MUMBLES)
It's really good.

08:32.148 --> 08:33.785
(IMITATES MUMBLE,
CHUCKLES)

08:37.956 --> 08:39.857
You're my favorite
person here.

08:45.766 --> 08:46.765
Well, uh...

08:49.000 --> 08:51.902
Us girls,
we gotta stick together
in this place.

08:58.372 --> 08:59.580
Yeah.

09:01.375 --> 09:03.584
(THUNDER RUMBLING)
(RAIN PATTERING)

09:07.920 --> 09:09.920
(WIND HOWLING)

09:21.131 --> 09:22.130
(SHUDDERING)

09:28.435 --> 09:29.808
(WHIMPERING SOFTLY)

09:30.844 --> 09:31.843
(WHIMPERING)

09:32.813 --> 09:34.043
(MUFFLED SCREAMS)

09:37.818 --> 09:38.817
(SIGHS)

10:15.020 --> 10:17.020
(UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING)

10:53.058 --> 10:54.057
(DOOR RATTLES)

10:58.492 --> 10:59.700
(BREATH TREMBLES)

11:02.397 --> 11:04.397
(ETHEREAL MUSIC PLAYING)

11:23.858 --> 11:25.451
ANN'S MOTHER:
(WHISPERING)<i> Annie.</i>

11:26.355 --> 11:27.354
(BABY CRIES IN DISTANCE)

11:34.000 --> 11:34.999
(BABY CONTINUES CRYING)

11:45.209 --> 11:46.813
ANN'S MOTHER:
<i> Annie, let go.</i>

11:53.052 --> 11:54.051
(SIGHS SOFTLY)

11:55.384 --> 11:56.383
(GASPS)

11:58.024 --> 11:59.221
Hey, Natalie.

12:00.829 --> 12:01.828
Hi.

12:02.897 --> 12:04.193
Are you feeling okay?

12:05.867 --> 12:07.361
I don't like
that room.

12:10.432 --> 12:12.201
How did you get out
of that room?

12:13.941 --> 12:15.204
I wanted to find you.

12:22.180 --> 12:24.213
Nougat is a family
of confections

12:24.248 --> 12:25.511
made with sugar
and honey,

12:25.546 --> 12:27.920
roasted nuts
and whipped egg whites.

12:28.549 --> 12:29.548
I looked it up.

12:32.124 --> 12:34.421
Did you know that
candies have families?

12:36.458 --> 12:37.457
I do now.

12:43.366 --> 12:44.937
Shall we head back
to your room?

12:46.468 --> 12:47.467
Okay.

13:05.652 --> 13:06.959
ANN'S MOTHER:
(WHISPERING)<i> Annie.</i>

13:13.935 --> 13:15.935
(PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING)

13:32.679 --> 13:34.217
<i> I'm here with you.</i>

13:34.252 --> 13:36.087
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYS)

13:36.122 --> 13:38.122
(EERIE FEMALE VOICE
SPEAKING BULGARIAN)

13:44.361 --> 13:47.362
(EERIE VOICE
SNARLS, WHINES)

13:51.368 --> 13:53.368
(EERIE VOICE RESUMES
SPEAKING BULGARIAN)

13:55.339 --> 13:57.339
(SHOUTING AGGRESSIVELY
IN BULGARIAN)

14:01.180 --> 14:03.114
(MAN ON VIDEO
SPEAKING BULGARIAN)

14:03.149 --> 14:05.116
(WOMAN ON VIDEO SNARLS)

14:05.151 --> 14:07.151
(MAN CONTINUES SPEAKING)

14:07.186 --> 14:09.087
(WOMAN LAUGHS, MOANS)

14:09.122 --> 14:10.924
(BOTH CONTINUE
SPEAKING BULGARIAN)

14:12.620 --> 14:15.489
(WOMAN BABBLING MOCKINGLY)

14:15.524 --> 14:18.525
(MAN CONTINUES SPEAKING)
(WOMAN CONTINUES BABBLING)

14:19.462 --> 14:20.461
(WOMAN SPEAKING)

14:21.596 --> 14:24.465
(WOMAN YELLING)

14:24.500 --> 14:28.568
(MAN SPEAKING)
(WOMAN SPEAKS SOFTLY)

14:28.603 --> 14:30.537
(REMOTE CLICKS)
(VIDEO STOPS)

14:30.572 --> 14:33.980
Elena had entered
the terminal stage
of possession here.

14:35.445 --> 14:37.412
She would tear
her own clothes,

14:37.447 --> 14:40.580
lick her own urine,
eat coal.

14:40.615 --> 14:43.055
In the terminal stage,

14:43.090 --> 14:49.358
the possessed reaches
the extremity of physical
and spiritual corruption.

14:49.393 --> 14:51.459
Deliverance
is still possible, but...

14:53.760 --> 14:54.968
death is imminent.

14:59.469 --> 15:01.073
Sadly for Elena,

15:02.109 --> 15:03.207
death came first.

15:07.411 --> 15:10.412
Demons
are Lucifer's
foot soldiers.

15:10.447 --> 15:13.283
They know no fatigue,
no fear, no doubt.

15:13.318 --> 15:16.715
When you enter the room
of the possessed,

15:16.750 --> 15:19.454
you are walking
onto a battlefield.

15:19.489 --> 15:21.654
The Devil will
try to distract you.

15:21.689 --> 15:23.359
Sow doubt in God's word.

15:24.263 --> 15:26.065
Always remember,

15:26.100 --> 15:28.034
the word of God

15:28.069 --> 15:30.366
is your most
powerful weapon.

15:33.272 --> 15:36.603
But the Rite is not just
a series of prayers.

15:38.739 --> 15:41.179
It's a dance.

15:41.214 --> 15:45.018
We have to feel
the cadence of the battle.

15:45.053 --> 15:46.283
Work with our partners.

15:47.649 --> 15:53.752
Understand the correct
entry points for attack.

15:53.787 --> 15:59.494
Regrettably, the priests
made fatal errors
in Elena's exorcism.

15:59.529 --> 16:01.760
What would you
have done differently?

16:01.795 --> 16:05.665
(PRIEST EXORCISING
IN BULGARIAN
ON EARPHONES)

16:05.700 --> 16:07.700
(ELENA SCREAMING
IN BULGARIAN
ON EARPHONES)

16:10.639 --> 16:12.639
(PRIEST AND ELENA
CONTINUE SPEAKING)

16:19.714 --> 16:21.615
(TRACKPAD CLICKS)
(AUDIO REWINDS)

16:21.650 --> 16:23.386
(TRACKPAD CLICKS)
(AUDIO RESUMES)

16:25.753 --> 16:27.324
(ELENA REPEATING PHRASE
IN BULGARIAN)

16:40.207 --> 16:43.043
ANN: My mother
talked about hearing
that voice inside.

16:44.541 --> 16:46.706
She said the voice
didn't really want her.

16:48.776 --> 16:50.215
It wanted me.

16:51.647 --> 16:54.714
Because I was one
of God's chosen soldiers.

16:56.850 --> 16:59.389
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)

17:03.824 --> 17:05.461
(READER TRILLS)
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

17:19.444 --> 17:20.476
Sister.

17:20.511 --> 17:21.576
Hi.

17:21.611 --> 17:23.446
I'm reviewing
some cases

17:23.481 --> 17:26.647
and there seems
to be some gaps
in the directory.

17:26.682 --> 17:29.353
The records
are entered directly
into the main archive.

17:29.388 --> 17:31.718
There are
no gaps.

17:31.753 --> 17:34.358
And what about
the terminal cases?

17:34.393 --> 17:35.854
Those are classified.

17:42.731 --> 17:44.896
FATHER QUINN:
<i> You summoned me, Sister?</i>

17:44.931 --> 17:48.438
SISTER EUPHEMIA:
I understand that Sister Ann
has taken it upon herself

17:48.473 --> 17:51.342
to attend
another one
of your classes.

17:51.377 --> 17:52.871
I wouldn't
say "attend."

17:52.906 --> 17:54.543
More like "infiltrate."

17:54.578 --> 17:56.611
She's very light
on her feet.

17:56.646 --> 17:59.383
The rules of the Church
are quite clear, Father.

17:59.418 --> 18:02.584
Only male clergy
may be enrolled
in exorcism training.

18:03.356 --> 18:04.916
For now.

18:04.951 --> 18:07.457
You should be
grateful, child.

18:07.492 --> 18:10.823
In years past,
even patient care
in exorcism school

18:10.858 --> 18:12.495
was restricted
to priests.

18:13.432 --> 18:15.597
Now here you stand.

18:15.632 --> 18:19.271
But what does it matter
if I'll never be able
to perform an exorcism?

18:19.306 --> 18:21.603
Is a nurse
of no benefit
to her patients

18:21.638 --> 18:24.474
because she can't
perform surgery?

18:24.509 --> 18:27.444
Female surgeons
were once unthinkable.

18:27.479 --> 18:28.841
Somebody had to be
the first.

18:29.811 --> 18:32.482
Yes. Well,

18:32.517 --> 18:35.320
healing the flesh
is a very different
undertaking

18:35.355 --> 18:37.883
than healing
the spirit.

18:37.918 --> 18:41.326
As members
of the Catholic
community of women,

18:41.361 --> 18:44.560
it is not our place
to free these souls
from their tormentors.

18:44.595 --> 18:46.661
We are here
to comfort,

18:46.696 --> 18:49.400
to pray,
and show mercy.

18:50.502 --> 18:51.501
That is all.

18:53.736 --> 18:55.703
You may return
to your duties now.

18:56.838 --> 18:57.837
Yes, Sister.

18:58.609 --> 18:59.608
Father.

19:06.617 --> 19:08.221
She wants
to learn.

19:09.521 --> 19:10.883
And I want to
protect her.

19:15.296 --> 19:17.692
(SHOWTUNES MUSIC PLAYING
ON SPEAKER)

19:21.533 --> 19:22.532
(HUMMING)

19:31.609 --> 19:33.609
(HUMMING ANN'S
MOTHER'S SONG)

19:39.452 --> 19:41.452
(CONTINUES HUMMING)

19:45.920 --> 19:47.656
Clark, how do you
know that song?

19:50.826 --> 19:51.825
(STOPS HUMMING)

19:54.401 --> 19:55.895
We've been waiting
for you.

19:59.736 --> 20:00.735
(FLESH SIZZLING)

20:05.071 --> 20:06.510
(STATIC CRACKLES)

20:06.545 --> 20:07.973
(ANN'S MOTHER HUMMING
ON SPEAKER)

20:09.680 --> 20:12.681
Your mother
has a pretty voice.

20:12.716 --> 20:14.617
(GASPING)
(CLARK HUMMING ALONG)

20:14.652 --> 20:15.651
(DOOR SLAMS)

20:16.852 --> 20:18.390
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLES)

20:18.425 --> 20:19.424
(CONTINUES HUMMING)

20:21.054 --> 20:22.559
(CLICKING)

20:22.594 --> 20:24.462
Hello, can anybody
hear me?

20:27.599 --> 20:28.862
(CHOKING)

20:28.897 --> 20:32.503
(IN DEMONIC VOICE)
Let me in.

20:32.538 --> 20:33.966
(SNARLING)

20:34.001 --> 20:35.000
(BOTH GRUNTING)

20:36.773 --> 20:37.838
(HUMMING CONTINUES
ON SPEAKER)

20:37.873 --> 20:38.872
(CLARK HUMMING ALONG)

20:40.007 --> 20:41.039
ANN: No!

20:41.074 --> 20:42.282
(LIGHTS CRACKLING)

20:45.518 --> 20:46.682
(LAUGHS MANIACALLY)

20:46.717 --> 20:47.617
(HUMMING CONTINUES
ON SPEAKER)

20:48.785 --> 20:49.784
ANN: No!

20:50.952 --> 20:52.622
(ANN PANTING)
(HUMMING STOPS)

20:57.563 --> 20:58.826
(TABLET BEEPS)

20:58.861 --> 20:59.695
CARDINAL MATTHEWS:
I've seen enough.

21:02.370 --> 21:06.372
This demon appeared
to go after Sister Ann
without cause.

21:06.407 --> 21:09.342
Provoked by her
mere presence.

21:09.377 --> 21:10.871
For her own protection,

21:10.906 --> 21:13.104
and that of
others here
at St. Michael's,

21:13.139 --> 21:15.975
we should
send her back
to the convent.

21:16.010 --> 21:19.715
Evil isn't confined
to the walls of
this institution.

21:19.750 --> 21:21.079
I'd feel better
having her here.

21:22.082 --> 21:23.554
I can work with her.

21:23.589 --> 21:24.720
Keep an eye on her.

21:24.755 --> 21:27.360
Work with her?
In what sense?

21:28.726 --> 21:30.726
I'd like to teach her,
Your Eminence.

21:32.730 --> 21:35.467
That's against
all precedent,

21:35.502 --> 21:36.666
all doctrine.

21:36.701 --> 21:38.437
FATHER QUINN:
Nothing formal.

21:38.472 --> 21:40.032
Just enough to
protect herself

21:40.870 --> 21:41.869
and others.

21:44.742 --> 21:47.842
I'm not sure
of the exact nature
of it.

21:47.877 --> 21:49.745
But this
relationship
she has...

21:51.617 --> 21:52.748
it's personal.

21:53.949 --> 21:55.553
But, Father,

21:55.588 --> 21:57.885
we all have a personal
relationship with God.

21:58.888 --> 21:59.887
(CLEARS THROAT)

22:01.088 --> 22:02.791
Not with God, Sister.

22:07.831 --> 22:08.830
With the Devil.

22:12.066 --> 22:14.066
(DARK MUSIC PLAYING)

22:35.760 --> 22:38.497
FATHER QUINN:
The citadel has fallen.

22:38.532 --> 22:40.763
The walls
have crumbled.

22:40.798 --> 22:42.897
Black smoke
blots out the sun.

22:44.230 --> 22:46.538
Because, as some of you
may already know,

22:46.573 --> 22:48.903
we have
a female student
in the class

22:49.741 --> 22:51.070
as an observer.

22:51.105 --> 22:53.138
Sister Ann will be
accompanying us

22:53.173 --> 22:55.140
on our rounds
for the rest
of the term.

22:57.078 --> 22:59.749
Now pay close attention.

22:59.784 --> 23:04.655
The nuances of our craft
require active learning
to truly understand.

23:05.251 --> 23:07.625
So, group one,

23:07.660 --> 23:10.826
let's descend into
the mouth of hell,
shall we?

23:10.861 --> 23:12.861
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)

23:18.737 --> 23:20.066
(READER TRILLS)
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

23:26.580 --> 23:28.580
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES)

23:32.817 --> 23:33.816
(READER TRILLS)

23:40.627 --> 23:43.595
FATHER QUINN:
Clear your minds of
all thoughts but prayer.

23:45.566 --> 23:46.829
You must remain resolute

23:47.964 --> 23:49.568
despite the distractions.

23:52.001 --> 23:54.870
It can be the difference
between life and death

23:54.905 --> 23:55.970
for both you...

23:57.611 --> 23:58.808
and the afflicted.

24:02.176 --> 24:04.748
The subject
is a recent admission.

24:04.783 --> 24:08.983
Dr. Peters'
preliminary diagnosis
was idiopathic epilepsy.

24:09.018 --> 24:11.887
The subject
was moved here
to observation

24:11.922 --> 24:13.592
when she began
to exhibit behavior

24:13.627 --> 24:16.089
that Dr. Peters
couldn't explain.

24:17.994 --> 24:20.027
Natalie is
10 years old.

24:20.062 --> 24:23.569
We have to act quickly
to halt any further
escalation.

24:24.264 --> 24:25.670
I need two volunteers.

24:33.339 --> 24:34.547
FATHER DANTE:
I'll go, Father.

24:36.243 --> 24:37.814
FATHER QUINN:
Very well.

24:37.849 --> 24:39.717
You will take
the lead.

24:39.752 --> 24:41.147
Who would like to
assist Father Dante?

24:43.789 --> 24:44.854
I will.

24:47.320 --> 24:48.594
Father Raymond.

24:50.763 --> 24:52.961
The armor of God.

24:52.996 --> 24:56.327
Each of you
have performed
a simple exorcism

24:56.362 --> 24:59.231
every time
you baptized a child.

24:59.266 --> 25:02.168
Cleansing them
of their original sin.

25:02.203 --> 25:04.775
That was baptism
by holy water.

25:05.745 --> 25:10.176
This is baptism
by fire.

25:10.211 --> 25:14.048
<i> Remember,</i>
<i> the name "Lucifer"</i>

25:14.083 --> 25:17.282
derives from
the Latin term
<i> "lucem ferre."</i>

25:18.186 --> 25:19.317
"Bringer of light."

25:21.090 --> 25:23.893
The Devil will
shine his light

25:23.928 --> 25:28.128
<i>into the darkest,</i>
<i>deepest recesses</i>
<i>of your mind,</i>

25:28.163 --> 25:30.900
exposing your
innermost secrets.

25:31.837 --> 25:33.804
Your deepest pain.

25:33.839 --> 25:37.610
He will use this pain
to break into your soul.

25:39.273 --> 25:40.910
(READER TRILLS)
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

25:55.927 --> 25:57.894
FATHER QUINN: (ON SPEAKER)
<i> You must look past the girl.</i>

25:57.929 --> 26:00.292
<i> She is as much demon</i>
<i> as victim.</i>

26:09.204 --> 26:13.041
<i> In Nomine Patris,</i>
<i> et Filii,</i>
<i> et Spiritus Sancti.</i>

26:13.076 --> 26:14.680
Amen.
Amen.

26:16.783 --> 26:18.783
(BONES CRACKING,
FLESH SQUELCHING)

26:23.449 --> 26:25.350
FATHER DANTE:
<i> Christ, have mercy.</i>

26:25.385 --> 26:27.088
Strike terror,

26:27.123 --> 26:29.893
Lord, into the beast
now defiling this
innocent child.

26:29.928 --> 26:31.796
Stretch out your
mighty hand, Lord.

26:31.831 --> 26:36.196
And cast this demon
out of your servant,
Natalie Hope.

26:36.231 --> 26:38.198
We cast you out.

26:38.233 --> 26:42.301
<i> ♪ I can't hear you ♪</i>

26:42.336 --> 26:43.368
(BONES CRACK)
(WINCES)

26:43.403 --> 26:45.073
No!
(FLESH SIZZLES)

26:45.108 --> 26:46.107
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

26:51.983 --> 26:53.785
(GROWLING, HISSING)

26:56.152 --> 26:57.382
Stay far from
this creature of God.

26:58.891 --> 27:00.154
BOTH: For it is He
who commands you.

27:00.189 --> 27:01.892
<i> He who flung</i>
<i> you headlong...</i>

27:01.927 --> 27:03.058
(AUDIO DISTORTS)

27:03.093 --> 27:04.224
(SWITCH CLANGS)

27:04.259 --> 27:06.666
FATHER DANTE: No.
Oh, shit.

27:08.197 --> 27:09.999
Father...
(SLURPING)

27:10.034 --> 27:11.429
Pray. Pray together.

27:13.103 --> 27:14.905
BOTH: For it is He
who commands you.

27:14.940 --> 27:17.138
Oh, he who flung you headlong
from the heights of Heaven

27:17.173 --> 27:18.370
into the depths
of Hell!
(SNARLING)

27:19.307 --> 27:20.746
(BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY)

27:20.781 --> 27:22.374
NATALIE: (WHISPERS)
<i> Una chica.</i>

27:22.409 --> 27:23.408
(BREATH TREMBLES)

27:26.182 --> 27:27.181
(SNARLING)

27:33.024 --> 27:34.826
(BONES CRACK)

27:34.861 --> 27:36.861
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

27:39.866 --> 27:42.130
FATHER QUINN:
<i> Don't stop.</i>
<i> Commit to the words.</i>

27:46.037 --> 27:48.433
For it is He
who commands you.

27:48.468 --> 27:51.106
He who flung you
headlong from the
heights of Heaven

27:51.141 --> 27:52.272
into the depths
of Hell.

27:54.078 --> 27:55.341
<i> Into the depths</i>
<i> of Hell.</i>

27:57.147 --> 27:58.146
(WHIMPERING)

28:07.355 --> 28:09.322
(DEMONIC GRUNTING,
SNARLING)

28:10.193 --> 28:11.192
(FLESH SQUELCHING)

28:15.902 --> 28:17.132
(NERVOUSLY)
It is He
who commands...

28:17.167 --> 28:18.903
(GROWLING INHUMANLY)

28:29.311 --> 28:30.310
(SNARLING)

28:33.051 --> 28:35.854
(IN DISTORTED VOICE)
Let me in!

28:38.452 --> 28:39.451
(GASPS)

28:40.520 --> 28:42.355
(GLASS SQUEAKS)
(DOOR OPENS)

28:44.425 --> 28:46.964
Lord, repel
this Devil's powers.

28:46.999 --> 28:49.197
By the incarnation,
passion, resurrection,

28:49.232 --> 28:50.935
<i> and ascension of</i>
<i> our Lord Jesus Christ,</i>

28:50.970 --> 28:54.268
I command you
to depart
this child of God.

28:55.040 --> 28:56.039
(INHUMAN SCREECH)

29:07.580 --> 29:08.854
(BED CREAKS)

29:11.958 --> 29:12.957
(SOFT GROWLING)

29:19.130 --> 29:20.129
(SOFT GROWLING CONTINUES)

29:31.912 --> 29:33.142
(YELPS, GRUNTS)

29:35.080 --> 29:36.079
FATHER DANTE:
<i> Father.</i>

29:37.951 --> 29:38.950
(BONES CRACKING)

29:44.089 --> 29:45.825
Say something.
Say something,
Father.

29:58.070 --> 29:59.135
Natalie.

30:00.303 --> 30:01.302
(HISSING)

30:06.606 --> 30:08.078
Natalie, can you hear me?

30:08.113 --> 30:09.112
(HISSING INHUMANLY)

30:10.049 --> 30:12.478
(STRAINING)

30:12.513 --> 30:15.217
Sister Ann,
don't deviate
from the scripture.

30:15.989 --> 30:16.988
ANN: Natalie.

30:19.355 --> 30:20.486
Natalie, I'm here.

30:23.095 --> 30:24.094
I'm here with you.

30:27.693 --> 30:28.901
(BREATH TREMBLING)

30:30.168 --> 30:31.530
(SHUDDERING)
I'm scared.

30:32.566 --> 30:34.401
Natalie, I'm here.

30:34.436 --> 30:35.534
(SHUDDERS, GRUNTS)

30:37.142 --> 30:38.141
(GASPS)

30:39.078 --> 30:40.077
(STIFLED SCREAMING)

30:40.574 --> 30:41.573
Go!

30:43.445 --> 30:44.444
(GAGS)

30:45.216 --> 30:46.215
Father.

30:47.515 --> 30:49.548
Give place,
abominable creature.

30:49.583 --> 30:50.681
Give way to Christ.

30:50.716 --> 30:52.925
(CHOKING, SCREAMING)

30:52.960 --> 30:54.388
You are a shield
about me,

30:54.423 --> 30:56.258
my glory,

30:56.293 --> 30:57.391
the lifter
of my head.

31:00.330 --> 31:02.165
Sister, with me now.

31:02.200 --> 31:04.266
BOTH: I cast you forth
into outer darkness

31:04.301 --> 31:06.697
where everlasting ruin
awaits you.

31:06.732 --> 31:07.940
(GURGLING)

31:10.439 --> 31:13.539
In the name of
our Lord Jesus Christ,
I cast you out.

31:16.478 --> 31:17.983
(GASPS)

31:18.018 --> 31:19.017
(PRIESTS GRUNT)

31:19.987 --> 31:21.019
(NATALIE WHEEZES)

31:21.054 --> 31:22.647
(GASPING HEAVILY)

31:26.257 --> 31:27.256
(COUGHING)

31:29.293 --> 31:30.358
Hey.

31:31.262 --> 31:32.261
(GASPING)

31:37.367 --> 31:39.103
Hi, sweetie.
It's okay.

31:40.535 --> 31:41.567
She's okay.

31:49.412 --> 31:50.411
(PANTING)

31:54.747 --> 31:57.616
I have to start wearing
adult diapers to class.

31:57.651 --> 31:59.156
(ANN LAUGHS)
You and me
both.

32:01.721 --> 32:02.720
To you.

32:05.560 --> 32:09.001
Hey, who knows what
would've happened if you
hadn't stepped in there.

32:09.036 --> 32:12.367
It's not a sin to take
a little victory lap, right?

32:12.402 --> 32:14.336
No, I thought
I got through to her.

32:14.371 --> 32:15.370
For...

32:15.801 --> 32:17.372
a moment.

32:17.407 --> 32:19.011
But...
FATHER DANTE:
Hey, you did.

32:19.046 --> 32:20.507
And it weakened
the demon

32:20.542 --> 32:22.982
'cause Natalie was
still in there somewhere.

32:24.348 --> 32:25.380
I don't know.

32:26.713 --> 32:28.713
If Father Quinn
hadn't stepped in...

32:30.486 --> 32:31.485
You okay?

32:33.621 --> 32:35.192
Uh, yeah.

32:42.168 --> 32:43.695
I think this was
meant for me.

32:45.699 --> 32:46.698
Why?

32:49.340 --> 32:51.307
My baby sister,
Emilia.

32:52.244 --> 32:53.243
She, uh...

32:54.411 --> 32:55.476
She was raped.

32:57.678 --> 32:58.677
She got pregnant.

33:01.154 --> 33:02.153
ANN: I'm so sorry.

33:04.751 --> 33:07.620
She, uh...
She lost the baby.

33:10.724 --> 33:12.361
She's been afflicted
ever since.

33:24.573 --> 33:25.572
(READER TRILLS)

33:41.788 --> 33:43.788
(UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING)

33:52.436 --> 33:53.501
(BUTTON CLICKS)

33:53.536 --> 33:54.667
(TRILLING)
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

34:52.364 --> 34:53.363
(SOFT THUDDING)

34:59.899 --> 35:00.898
(GASPS SOFTLY)

35:02.935 --> 35:04.143
(GASPS)

35:08.512 --> 35:09.511
(BREATH TREMBLING)

35:16.289 --> 35:17.288
(SIGHS)

35:18.852 --> 35:19.851
(GASPS)

35:22.922 --> 35:23.921
(BREATH TREMBLING)

35:33.900 --> 35:35.537
(READER TRILLS)
(DOOR UNLOCKS)

35:55.328 --> 35:56.327
(WHIMPERING)

36:05.899 --> 36:06.898
NATALIE: Hi.
(GASPS)

36:10.970 --> 36:12.508
How are you feeling?

36:13.610 --> 36:15.379
(GROGGILY)
Kinda sleepy.

36:18.945 --> 36:20.516
This isn't my room.

36:22.619 --> 36:23.618
No.

36:26.821 --> 36:28.656
This is a special room.

36:31.331 --> 36:32.825
I had a bad dream.

36:34.829 --> 36:36.334
I'm sorry.

36:38.569 --> 36:40.833
Can you tell me what
you remember about it?

36:43.772 --> 36:46.476
I was in a room.

36:46.511 --> 36:48.610
It was kinda
like this room.

36:48.645 --> 36:49.644
And...

36:50.614 --> 36:51.943
there were people.

36:51.978 --> 36:53.318
They were all yelling.

36:55.355 --> 36:56.882
Were they yelling at you?

36:58.688 --> 37:01.920
Couldn't understand
most of them.

37:01.955 --> 37:04.593
I think they were talking
to someone else.

37:05.860 --> 37:06.925
Who?

37:08.995 --> 37:09.994
(SNIFFLES)

37:10.634 --> 37:11.798
The voice.

37:14.374 --> 37:15.505
Whose voice?

37:17.476 --> 37:19.608
He tells me things.

37:19.643 --> 37:21.808
Promises me things.

37:21.843 --> 37:23.040
Sometimes...

37:24.846 --> 37:26.549
he shows me things.

37:27.948 --> 37:29.651
They're bad.

37:29.686 --> 37:31.719
It's all right.

37:31.754 --> 37:32.819
You can tell me.

37:35.725 --> 37:37.593
You were there.

37:37.628 --> 37:39.661
(LOW OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

37:39.696 --> 37:40.695
But...

37:42.798 --> 37:44.600
you weren't yelling.

37:48.573 --> 37:49.572
Natalie?

37:57.945 --> 37:59.615
ANN:<i> Natalie wasn't</i>
<i> cleansed, was she?</i>

38:00.618 --> 38:02.783
We're not sure.

38:02.818 --> 38:04.884
The demon may
have undertaken
temporary refuge.

38:06.492 --> 38:08.019
Will the Rite be
administered again?

38:09.594 --> 38:12.056
The girl
will remain in
observation.

38:12.091 --> 38:13.761
If she escalates
further,

38:13.796 --> 38:16.093
it may be beyond
our capacity
to deal with.

38:17.668 --> 38:19.096
She'll be transferred
to the Vatican.

38:21.606 --> 38:23.540
You mean
she might be
a terminal case?

38:31.011 --> 38:33.077
I want to stay
with her, Father.

38:33.112 --> 38:34.782
I've made
a connection.

38:34.817 --> 38:37.422
That's exactly
the problem.

38:37.457 --> 38:40.920
The exorcist
is a confessor
and an intercessor,

38:40.955 --> 38:41.954
not a friend.

38:43.529 --> 38:45.463
But what if
I can help her?

38:45.498 --> 38:49.060
Terminal cases
are the most complex
and delicate we face.

38:49.095 --> 38:52.437
They can only be
handled by the most
skilled exorcists.

38:56.003 --> 38:57.574
If you want
to help her,

38:58.808 --> 39:01.171
pray.

39:01.206 --> 39:04.581
Your power
is in the spirit.
Not the flesh.

39:06.684 --> 39:08.618
She may still make
a full recovery.

39:13.053 --> 39:15.053
(PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING)
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

40:02.707 --> 40:05.642
Sister, Cardinal Matthews
is requesting this urgently.

40:19.988 --> 40:21.988
(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)

41:15.846 --> 41:16.845
(DISTORTED SCREAMS)

41:37.934 --> 41:40.000
MALE INTERVIEWER:
<i>So, what happened</i>
<i>when the soldiers</i>

41:40.035 --> 41:41.969
<i>came to your house</i>
<i>that day?</i>

41:42.004 --> 41:45.335
<i> It was me</i>
<i> and my two</i>
<i> younger sisters.</i>

41:45.370 --> 41:48.976
<i> They said</i>
<i> one of us could go.</i>
<i> I ran.</i>

41:49.011 --> 41:52.947
<i> I didn't wait</i>
<i> for anything.</i>
<i> I just ran.</i>

41:52.982 --> 41:54.179
INTERVIEWER:
<i>You ran away and...</i>

41:54.214 --> 41:56.115
<i>and the soldiers</i>
<i>shot your sisters?</i>

41:57.723 --> 41:59.756
MILA:<i> Yes.</i>

41:59.791 --> 42:01.989
INTERVIEWER:
<i> Mila, tell me about</i>
<i> the voice that you heard.</i>

42:03.355 --> 42:06.191
<i> I kept hearing</i>
<i> those shots.</i>

42:06.226 --> 42:09.293
<i> The demon spoke to me</i>
<i> in the sound</i>
<i> of those gunshots.</i>

42:09.328 --> 42:10.965
<i> He took control.</i>

42:12.100 --> 42:14.166
INTERVIEWER:<i> Okay.</i>

42:14.201 --> 42:15.904
<i>But then you</i>
<i>were cleansed,</i>
<i>right?</i>

42:15.939 --> 42:17.070
<i>You received</i>
<i>the Rite of Exorcism.</i>

42:17.875 --> 42:19.842
<i>And you were healed.</i>

42:19.877 --> 42:20.876
<i> "Healed"?</i>

42:26.378 --> 42:27.916
(FLESH RIPPING)
(WINCING)

42:33.220 --> 42:35.253
<i> I kept cutting,</i>

42:35.288 --> 42:37.288
<i> but the body</i>
<i> is still here.</i>

42:38.929 --> 42:41.061
INTERVIEWER:
<i>You did that</i>
<i>to yourself?</i>

42:41.096 --> 42:43.129
<i> I prayed for</i>
<i> God's forgiveness.</i>

42:43.164 --> 42:47.870
<i> I prayed and I prayed,</i>
<i> but deep down I knew.</i>

42:47.905 --> 42:50.004
<i> I didn't deserve</i>
<i> forgiveness.</i>

42:59.686 --> 43:01.917
My mother felt guilt
for what she had done.

43:04.383 --> 43:05.888
I was alone with her.

43:05.923 --> 43:07.725
ANN'S MOTHER:<i> Annie?</i>

43:07.760 --> 43:09.826
Where are you?
(SHUDDERING)

43:09.861 --> 43:11.861
(OBJECT THUDS)

43:11.896 --> 43:13.962
(FLOORBOARD CREAKS)
(MUFFLED FOOTSTEPS)

43:13.997 --> 43:15.194
Annie?

43:16.901 --> 43:18.901
(FOOTSTEPS THUMPING)
(OBJECT THUDS)

43:21.334 --> 43:22.938
(ANGRILY) Annie!
(OBJECT CLATTERS)

43:24.469 --> 43:25.677
(DISHES CLATTERING)

43:29.881 --> 43:30.880
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

43:35.755 --> 43:36.754
(GASPS)

43:41.255 --> 43:42.958
(COMB TEETH CLICKING)

43:46.766 --> 43:48.194
(YOUNG ANN GRUNTS, SCREAMS)

43:51.232 --> 43:53.870
(YOUNG ANN SCREAMS)

43:53.905 --> 43:56.169
DR. PETERS:
What you're describing
is terrifying.

43:56.204 --> 43:57.302
It's traumatic.

43:59.009 --> 44:01.944
Memories like these
are so hard to face.

44:05.818 --> 44:08.148
Your mother,
she eventually...

44:10.185 --> 44:11.723
She took her own life.

44:14.992 --> 44:18.125
DR. PETERS:<i> And you felt</i>
<i> responsible for her death.</i>

44:18.160 --> 44:20.798
That's a common
trauma response, Ann.

44:20.833 --> 44:22.998
For the victim
to feel shame.

44:24.463 --> 44:27.266
And the only way
to disarm these memories

44:27.301 --> 44:29.070
is to drag them
into the light.

44:30.106 --> 44:31.908
Confront the trauma.

44:34.374 --> 44:36.374
(THUNDER RUMBLING)
(PEOPLE SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)

44:40.952 --> 44:41.951
(READER TRILLS)

44:44.516 --> 44:45.889
(TRILLS)

44:45.924 --> 44:46.923
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

44:48.795 --> 44:49.893
WOMAN: What're you
doing down here?

44:49.928 --> 44:51.323
What's going on
with Natalie?

44:51.358 --> 44:53.160
They restricted
access.

44:53.195 --> 44:54.194
Why?

44:54.867 --> 44:56.295
No idea.

44:56.330 --> 44:57.736
Maybe they're
transferring her.

45:09.244 --> 45:11.244
(LOW OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

45:16.284 --> 45:17.283
Father Dante.

45:19.419 --> 45:20.418
ANN: Hi.

45:22.554 --> 45:23.993
FATHER QUINN:
Right.

45:24.028 --> 45:25.324
Father.

45:25.359 --> 45:27.491
You can't let Natalie
be transferred.

45:27.526 --> 45:29.328
I've seen the records.

45:29.363 --> 45:32.430
The mortality rate
for terminal cases
is over 90%.

45:32.465 --> 45:35.103
Our faith
does not reside
in statistics, Sister.

45:35.138 --> 45:36.401
No. No, it doesn't.

45:36.436 --> 45:38.205
But I don't think
that it resides strictly

45:38.240 --> 45:39.437
in the word
of the Rite either.

45:40.946 --> 45:42.341
No?

45:42.376 --> 45:44.178
The Rite has
stood for millennia

45:44.213 --> 45:46.312
as the received
word of God.

45:46.347 --> 45:48.820
And you have notes?

45:48.855 --> 45:51.317
Where did you read
these records anyway?

45:51.352 --> 45:53.517
I know,
I broke the rules.

45:53.552 --> 45:58.225
But there is a lonely,
frightened little girl
at the center of this.

45:58.260 --> 45:59.358
You tread on
precarious ground

45:59.393 --> 46:01.162
when you make
this fight personal.

46:01.197 --> 46:03.593
But it is
personal, Father.
That is the point.

46:03.628 --> 46:07.938
You said yourself
that exorcism
is about nuance.

46:07.973 --> 46:09.907
And yet,
we have never
even considered it

46:09.942 --> 46:11.205
from the victim's
perspective.

46:11.240 --> 46:12.602
So what does
the demon want?

46:12.637 --> 46:14.846
It wants to dehumanize
the possessed

46:14.881 --> 46:17.442
and make them feel
unworthy of God's love.

46:17.477 --> 46:20.148
Our goal should be to
connect with the possessed

46:20.183 --> 46:22.887
and help them fight
for their own humanity.

46:22.922 --> 46:27.155
Let them know
we see them,
not just the demon.

46:27.190 --> 46:32.622
Is it not possible
that there are cases,
unique cases,

46:32.657 --> 46:34.459
that the Rite
cannot account for?

46:36.463 --> 46:39.398
What makes
these cases unique?

46:39.433 --> 46:43.501
Cases where the victim's
shame and guilt
are so profound

46:43.536 --> 46:45.338
that they invite
the demon in.

46:45.373 --> 46:47.241
And they want to suffer.

46:47.276 --> 46:48.473
They surrender control.

46:51.148 --> 46:52.510
(SIGHS)

46:52.545 --> 46:55.381
So where does
Natalie's shame
come from? Hmm?

46:55.416 --> 46:57.185
She is
an innocent child.

46:59.387 --> 47:01.255
(SOFTLY)
I don't know.

47:01.290 --> 47:05.391
Lucifer was once
the most beautiful and
powerful angel in Heaven.

47:05.426 --> 47:07.426
But he became prideful
and God cast him out.

47:07.461 --> 47:09.934
That...
That's it, Sister.

47:09.969 --> 47:12.497
I believe in you,
more than you can imagine.

47:12.532 --> 47:16.402
But you
have to understand
the danger here.

47:16.437 --> 47:20.604
If you shun the Church
to follow your own will,

47:20.639 --> 47:24.575
you will find yourself
wandering in the darkness.

47:25.985 --> 47:26.984
Alone.

47:30.319 --> 47:31.318
Father.

47:41.462 --> 47:43.198
I heard what you said.

47:43.233 --> 47:44.364
ANN: They can't
let Natalie
be transferred.

47:44.399 --> 47:45.629
She won't
come back.
I agree.

47:45.664 --> 47:46.971
And we don't
have much time.

47:47.699 --> 47:49.941
What do you mean?

47:49.976 --> 47:53.076
So, what if there was a way
that you could prove to them
that you're right.

47:54.475 --> 47:55.947
Your sister.

47:55.982 --> 47:58.543
She's possessed, Ann.
I know she is.

47:58.578 --> 48:01.414
And her episodes just
keep getting worse.

48:01.449 --> 48:04.021
I tried to have her
admitted here, but...

48:05.222 --> 48:07.585
it's complicated
for the Church.

48:07.620 --> 48:09.290
Because of her baby.

48:09.325 --> 48:11.061
She's devout.
Ann, you talk
about guilt.

48:11.096 --> 48:13.063
She had to make
an impossible
decision.

48:13.098 --> 48:14.592
And it's eating away
at her.

48:16.134 --> 48:18.728
She let the demon in.

48:18.763 --> 48:23.106
You want to attempt
an unauthorized exorcism?

48:24.736 --> 48:25.944
Not alone.

48:27.607 --> 48:30.047
Please, Ann.
(SIGHS)

48:30.082 --> 48:31.411
My sister
doesn't have
much time left.

48:31.446 --> 48:33.446
And I saw you
with Natalie.

48:33.481 --> 48:34.678
You have a gift.

48:34.713 --> 48:36.416
You connect
with the possessed.

48:36.451 --> 48:39.683
You see past the demon
and into the person.

48:39.718 --> 48:41.256
If you really believe
what you're saying...

48:41.291 --> 48:43.555
Natalie is still possessed.

48:43.590 --> 48:44.963
And she's still alive.

48:50.168 --> 48:51.167
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

49:03.115 --> 49:04.114
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

49:11.057 --> 49:12.386
(GASPS)
Hi, Mama.

49:15.424 --> 49:16.456
<i> Mi hijo.</i>

49:22.167 --> 49:23.166
(DOOR CREAKS)

49:31.473 --> 49:33.671
FATHER DANTE:
My mother says she's been
asleep for three days.

49:50.756 --> 49:51.788
(WHISPERS)
Are you ready?

49:53.198 --> 49:54.197
Are you?

50:00.700 --> 50:02.700
(LOW OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

50:10.578 --> 50:11.577
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

50:37.836 --> 50:40.375
(INHALES DEEPLY, WHEEZES)

50:44.150 --> 50:45.149
(RAGGED BREATHING)

50:55.656 --> 50:57.392
(WINCING)

50:57.427 --> 50:58.492
(GROANING CONVULSIVELY)

51:14.873 --> 51:16.576
(SHUSHES)

51:16.611 --> 51:17.610
(GROANING CONVULSIVELY)

51:24.190 --> 51:25.189
(SHUDDERING)

51:33.496 --> 51:34.495
(CONTINUES SHUDDERING)

51:39.238 --> 51:40.237
(SHUDDERING STOPS)

51:46.542 --> 51:47.541
(BREATHES HEAVILY)

51:49.314 --> 51:51.908
<i> Chiquita,</i> this is...

51:51.943 --> 51:54.746
This is Ann.
She's here
to help you. Okay?

51:55.386 --> 51:56.385
Emilia.

51:57.883 --> 51:58.882
Can you hear me?

52:00.985 --> 52:02.754
(WHISPERING)
It won't stop.

52:04.428 --> 52:05.427
The voice?

52:07.563 --> 52:10.861
It has no power over you
that you don't give it.

52:13.899 --> 52:14.898
Okay.

52:18.475 --> 52:20.970
"Blessed is the one
whose transgressions
are forgiven,

52:21.005 --> 52:22.906
whose sins
are covered."

52:22.941 --> 52:25.447
"Blessed is the one
whose sin the Lord
does not count against them,

52:25.482 --> 52:27.581
"and in whose spirit
is no deceit."

52:29.783 --> 52:34.951
You know what it feels like
to have something growing
inside you.

52:35.789 --> 52:37.459
Don't you, Sister?

52:39.727 --> 52:40.726
(WHIRRING HEAVILY)

52:42.367 --> 52:43.366
Yes.

52:45.898 --> 52:47.667
At least
this bitch knew

52:47.702 --> 52:50.274
(VOICE DISTORTING)
who the baby's
father was.

52:51.838 --> 52:52.837
(CHUCKLING)

52:55.039 --> 52:56.577
(WIND GUSTS)
(GASPS)

52:58.680 --> 53:00.416
(BONES CRACK)
(GRUNTS)

53:02.750 --> 53:03.749
(GRUNTING IN PAIN)

53:06.017 --> 53:07.225
(SCREAMS)

53:08.492 --> 53:09.491
(GRUNTING IN PAIN)

53:13.497 --> 53:15.926
(BREATHES RAPIDLY, SCREAMS)

53:15.961 --> 53:17.829
Help me!
(SQUEALING IN PAIN)

53:20.702 --> 53:22.504
Please! Please!

53:22.539 --> 53:24.308
(SQUEALING)

53:24.343 --> 53:25.969
(FLESH SQUELCHES)
(EMILIA GASPING)

53:27.940 --> 53:29.643
(DISTORTED GRUNTING)

53:38.786 --> 53:39.785
(CHUCKLES)

53:41.525 --> 53:43.327
Emilia, listen to me.

53:43.362 --> 53:44.889
Focus on the sound
of my voice.

53:44.924 --> 53:47.562
DEMON:<i> She can't hear you.</i>

53:47.597 --> 53:49.696
(GASPS)

53:49.731 --> 53:52.897
Emilia, the demon
preys on
the most devout

53:52.932 --> 53:55.636
because our guilt,
it is the deepest.

53:55.671 --> 53:56.670
(SCREAMS)

54:00.610 --> 54:01.741
Ann...

54:01.776 --> 54:02.775
(MUFFLED GROWLING)

54:05.351 --> 54:06.350
(EMILIA GASPING)

54:08.486 --> 54:10.079
ANN: Open your eyes.

54:10.114 --> 54:12.917
This flesh... This flesh
is yours. It is not his.
(GROANS)

54:12.952 --> 54:15.425
You don't
have to hide
from it anymore.

54:15.460 --> 54:17.823
I know you wanted
the baby to be gone.

54:17.858 --> 54:19.022
(MUFFLED SQUELCHING)

54:19.057 --> 54:21.024
You wanted it
to be over.

54:21.059 --> 54:22.366
Like you did?

54:24.601 --> 54:25.600
(SNIFFLES)

54:26.372 --> 54:28.064
Yes.

54:28.099 --> 54:30.869
Ann...
I know despair.

54:30.904 --> 54:33.443
How shame gets in
and rips you open.

54:33.478 --> 54:35.346
It's always there
and it just grows.

54:35.381 --> 54:36.380
Ann.

54:36.976 --> 54:38.613
(FLESH SQUELCHES)

54:38.648 --> 54:39.944
Psalm 86:5.

54:43.048 --> 54:44.916
"For you, O Lord,
are good and forgiving,

54:44.951 --> 54:47.083
"abounding
in steadfast love
to all who call..."

54:47.118 --> 54:49.085
He can never shut out
God's love for you.

54:50.121 --> 54:51.923
Don't hide from it.

54:51.958 --> 54:53.463
All of the pain.

54:54.961 --> 54:57.863
Follow me
into the pain.
We'll go there together.

54:57.898 --> 55:02.439
"For you, O Lord,
are good and forgiving..."
(CONTINUES INDISTINCTLY)

55:02.474 --> 55:04.936
Confess to yourself
and you will be forgiven.

55:08.106 --> 55:09.105
(EMILIA GASPING)

55:11.615 --> 55:12.977
(MUFFLED DEMONIC GROAN)

55:14.684 --> 55:15.683
(WHEEZES)

55:17.522 --> 55:18.884
(EMILIA CRIES)

55:19.854 --> 55:20.853
(BREATH SHAKING)

55:21.757 --> 55:23.427
(WHIMPERS)

55:23.462 --> 55:24.461
How did you do...

55:26.696 --> 55:27.695
(CONTINUES CRYING)

55:30.997 --> 55:31.996
It's over.

55:33.604 --> 55:34.933
Emilia, you're free.

55:34.968 --> 55:35.967
(CRYING CONTINUES)

55:37.806 --> 55:39.102
You freed yourself.

55:47.552 --> 55:48.848
That tattoo
above your wrist...

55:49.785 --> 55:50.817
is that a gang thing?

55:52.854 --> 55:53.886
It was, yeah.

56:00.158 --> 56:02.026
I got pregnant
when I was 15.

56:04.602 --> 56:07.097
Was too wasted
to remember
who the father was.

56:09.068 --> 56:11.640
They kicked me out
of my foster home.

56:11.675 --> 56:14.676
And by God's grace,
I found my way
to the shelter

56:14.711 --> 56:16.678
run by the
Sisters of St. Mary.

56:17.978 --> 56:19.142
And they
took me in.

56:20.145 --> 56:21.144
Cared for me.

56:22.851 --> 56:23.949
What about the baby?

56:27.152 --> 56:29.493
(BABY COOING)

56:29.528 --> 56:31.627
ANN:<i> The sisters arranged</i>
<i> for her adoption.</i>

56:36.700 --> 56:39.195
<i> I only held her</i>
<i> for a moment.</i>

56:39.230 --> 56:40.438
<i> But I, uh...</i>

56:41.540 --> 56:43.199
(BABY CRIES)

56:43.234 --> 56:44.871
<i> I've carried her with me</i>
<i> ever since.</i>

56:46.710 --> 56:47.709
(BABY CONTINUES CRYING)

56:52.012 --> 56:53.011
(CRYING)

56:55.653 --> 56:57.015
I abandoned her.

56:59.525 --> 57:00.689
And I pray that...

57:02.528 --> 57:03.890
that God can forgive me.

57:14.705 --> 57:16.507
"For you, O Lord,
are good...

57:18.203 --> 57:19.202
"and forgiving."

57:20.744 --> 57:22.106
(SIGHS)
Hey.

57:23.879 --> 57:24.944
He already has.

57:29.720 --> 57:31.720
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

57:33.559 --> 57:34.558
(RAIN PATTERING)

57:36.320 --> 57:38.529
(PENSIVE MUSIC PLAYING)

57:57.044 --> 57:58.043
(GRUNTING SOFTLY)

58:05.118 --> 58:06.183
(ANN'S MOTHER SOBS)

58:06.218 --> 58:09.021
(COMB TEETH CLICKING)

58:09.056 --> 58:11.056
(PENSIVE MUSIC CONTINUES)

58:17.702 --> 58:18.734
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

58:18.769 --> 58:20.670
(THUNDER CONTINUES RUMBLING)

58:20.705 --> 58:22.265
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

58:27.239 --> 58:28.238
(WINCING)

58:49.063 --> 58:50.062
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

58:53.738 --> 58:54.737
(GASPING)

59:01.845 --> 59:02.844
(FAUCET RUNS)

59:10.953 --> 59:12.183
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

59:18.697 --> 59:20.631
Cardinal Matthews
is calling for you.

59:24.164 --> 59:25.801
Yes, Sister.

59:25.836 --> 59:27.836
(SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING)

59:50.157 --> 59:51.156
Your Eminence.

59:52.830 --> 59:56.161
I'm afraid I have
some tragic news.

59:56.196 --> 59:59.736
Father Dante's sister,
Emilia, took her own life
last night.

1:00:00.772 --> 1:00:01.969
What?

1:00:02.004 --> 1:00:04.037
Emilia's mother
reported to the parish

1:00:04.072 --> 1:00:07.304
that you attempted
an exorcism on her.

1:00:08.813 --> 1:00:09.812
Is this true?

1:00:13.180 --> 1:00:14.916
I'm so sorry.

1:00:16.150 --> 1:00:17.820
CARDINAL MATTHEWS:
Then it is true.

1:00:17.855 --> 1:00:19.217
Yes, I thought that I...

1:00:19.252 --> 1:00:21.857
You thought
you knew better
than a church

1:00:21.892 --> 1:00:24.255
that has stood
for thousands
of years?

1:00:24.290 --> 1:00:25.388
Of course not.

1:00:25.423 --> 1:00:28.094
You overestimated
your competence

1:00:28.129 --> 1:00:31.163
and stepped right
into the Devil's snare.

1:00:31.198 --> 1:00:34.001
Please. It wasn't
Sister Ann's fault.

1:00:34.036 --> 1:00:36.839
I was desperate.

1:00:36.874 --> 1:00:39.710
You weren't remotely
prepared to take on
an exorcism like this.

1:00:40.273 --> 1:00:42.306
Demons retreat

1:00:42.341 --> 1:00:44.275
to avoid
further assault.

1:00:45.817 --> 1:00:47.146
It was a deception.

1:00:48.787 --> 1:00:49.918
Not a defeat.

1:00:49.953 --> 1:00:51.821
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

1:00:51.856 --> 1:00:54.285
You've both
betrayed the trust
the Church put in you.

1:00:54.320 --> 1:00:57.288
That I advocated for.

1:01:00.491 --> 1:01:02.898
I think...
(BREATH TREMBLING)

1:01:02.933 --> 1:01:06.132
I think it's best
if I return to my place
with the Sisters of St. Mary.

1:01:20.984 --> 1:01:22.984
(SOMBER MUSIC CONTINUES)

1:01:43.237 --> 1:01:44.236
(LEAVES RUSTLING)

1:01:59.253 --> 1:02:00.252
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

1:02:01.552 --> 1:02:02.760
Come in.

1:02:06.425 --> 1:02:07.831
Thank you
for seeing me.

1:02:10.363 --> 1:02:11.362
(DOOR CLOSES)

1:02:12.970 --> 1:02:14.299
(SIGHS) Well,

1:02:15.302 --> 1:02:17.566
this is grim.

1:02:17.601 --> 1:02:21.240
Although, apparently,
the abbess,
Benedetta Carlini,

1:02:21.275 --> 1:02:25.915
spent the last 35 years
of her life in a 6-by-6 hole
in the ground.

1:02:25.950 --> 1:02:30.216
On her dying day,
she said she never had
a moment's regret.

1:02:30.251 --> 1:02:32.020
I didn't realize
you were so familiar

1:02:32.055 --> 1:02:35.320
with the lexicon
of Catholic mystics.

1:02:35.355 --> 1:02:37.157
I'm an academic.

1:02:37.192 --> 1:02:38.521
I like to hear
both sides.

1:02:41.130 --> 1:02:43.097
I heard about
what happened.

1:02:44.463 --> 1:02:46.034
Father Dante's sister.

1:02:47.565 --> 1:02:49.499
I really thought
I'd gotten through
to her.

1:02:54.044 --> 1:02:55.109
I came...

1:02:57.883 --> 1:02:58.915
to give you this.

1:03:04.615 --> 1:03:08.221
ANN:
"Brain, mind, and body
in the healing of...

1:03:08.256 --> 1:03:10.487
"trauma."

1:03:10.522 --> 1:03:12.225
I know you're
a one book kinda gal,

1:03:12.260 --> 1:03:15.294
but I thought
you might enjoy some
light exile reading.

1:03:15.329 --> 1:03:16.328
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

1:03:18.464 --> 1:03:19.463
Ann.

1:03:20.499 --> 1:03:23.137
I've had patients that...

1:03:23.172 --> 1:03:25.436
no matter
how hard I tried,

1:03:25.471 --> 1:03:26.943
I couldn't save them.

1:03:33.149 --> 1:03:35.611
You might be
relieved to know that
Natalie was released.

1:03:38.352 --> 1:03:39.989
What?

1:03:40.024 --> 1:03:41.617
She was cleared
after observation,

1:03:41.652 --> 1:03:43.619
and she went home
with her mother
this morning.

1:03:44.358 --> 1:03:45.357
(CHUCKLES)

1:03:46.690 --> 1:03:47.898
(SNIFFLES)

1:03:49.297 --> 1:03:50.296
(SIGHS IN RELIEF)

1:03:52.531 --> 1:03:54.971
You're on a new path.

1:03:55.006 --> 1:03:56.434
It's natural
to feel lost.

1:03:58.240 --> 1:03:59.404
(SOFTLY) Keep going.

1:04:16.654 --> 1:04:17.653
(DOOR CLOSES)

1:04:32.076 --> 1:04:33.075
Father Dante.

1:04:34.738 --> 1:04:35.946
Sister Ann.

1:04:38.709 --> 1:04:39.917
What're you
doing here?

1:04:42.515 --> 1:04:44.350
Something's happened
at the school.

1:04:46.552 --> 1:04:47.551
Natalie.

1:04:50.424 --> 1:04:51.423
Walk with me.

1:04:54.758 --> 1:04:56.692
She suffered
a sudden relapse

1:04:56.727 --> 1:04:58.331
and they
rushed her back.

1:04:58.366 --> 1:05:00.036
(GRUNTING)
(SIRENS WAILING)

1:05:02.667 --> 1:05:04.205
(BONES CRACK)
(MAN SCREAMS)

1:05:11.643 --> 1:05:12.642
(EKG FLATLINING)

1:05:17.649 --> 1:05:20.188
FATHER DANTE:
<i>A priest and two</i>
<i>orderlies were killed.</i>

1:05:22.060 --> 1:05:26.128
I will pray for their souls
and for Natalie's deliverance.

1:05:26.163 --> 1:05:28.196
She's a terminal case.
She'll be transferred
back to Rome.

1:05:28.231 --> 1:05:30.297
No, we don't have
time for that.

1:05:30.332 --> 1:05:33.597
She has hours left,
not days.

1:05:33.632 --> 1:05:36.270
<i>They moved her to</i>
<i>the catacombs beneath</i>
<i>the main building.</i>

1:05:36.305 --> 1:05:38.503
They still have
holding cells there.

1:05:38.538 --> 1:05:40.340
Holding cells?

1:05:40.375 --> 1:05:41.704
Part of
the original structure.

1:05:43.642 --> 1:05:46.478
They have her
totally sealed away from
the rest of the academy.

1:05:48.086 --> 1:05:50.152
I don't think
they're willing
to risk more lives

1:05:50.187 --> 1:05:52.121
to attempt
another exorcism.

1:05:52.156 --> 1:05:53.155
Why?

1:05:54.719 --> 1:05:56.290
Why come
and tell me this?

1:05:58.228 --> 1:05:59.689
Because she gave me this.

1:06:06.764 --> 1:06:08.764
(SINISTER MUSIC PLAYING)

1:06:20.844 --> 1:06:23.746
I got this
when I first arrived here
at St. Mary's.

1:06:26.454 --> 1:06:29.158
And I wrapped it
around the wrist
of my little girl

1:06:29.193 --> 1:06:30.654
the day I gave her away.

1:06:40.864 --> 1:06:42.072
Father.

1:06:43.768 --> 1:06:45.273
Natalie is
my daughter.

1:06:48.113 --> 1:06:50.113
The demon
is using her

1:06:51.413 --> 1:06:52.544
<i> to get to me.</i>

1:06:55.252 --> 1:06:57.219
I can't let her
suffer for me.

1:06:58.849 --> 1:07:00.057
I won't.

1:07:02.292 --> 1:07:04.292
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)
(DARK MUSIC PLAYING)

1:07:08.166 --> 1:07:09.165
(BABY CRYING)

1:07:16.141 --> 1:07:20.374
Most glorious Prince
of the heavenly armies,
Michael the Archangel.

1:07:22.444 --> 1:07:26.347
<i> Defend us in battle</i>

1:07:26.382 --> 1:07:29.713
<i> against</i>
<i> principalities</i>
<i> and powers.</i>

1:07:32.883 --> 1:07:35.455
<i> Against the rulers</i>
<i> of darkness</i>
<i> in this world...</i>

1:07:40.429 --> 1:07:42.528
<i> against the spirits</i>
<i> of wickedness...</i>

1:07:45.929 --> 1:07:47.401
<i> in these high places.</i>

1:07:50.274 --> 1:07:52.142
<i> May Thy mercy descend</i>
<i> upon us, Lord.</i>

1:07:55.609 --> 1:07:56.608
<i> Amen.</i>

1:08:05.586 --> 1:08:06.618
(READER TRILLS)

1:08:09.425 --> 1:08:11.425
(FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING)

1:08:22.273 --> 1:08:23.272
(WATER DRIPPING)

1:08:37.387 --> 1:08:39.387
(FOREBODING MUSIC CONTINUES)

1:08:47.694 --> 1:08:49.694
ANN: Is that
holy water?

1:08:49.729 --> 1:08:51.201
FATHER DANTE: Yeah.

1:08:51.236 --> 1:08:52.367
It's the baptismal well.

1:09:21.992 --> 1:09:24.333
PRIESTS: ...spirits,
demonic forces,

1:09:24.368 --> 1:09:27.864
satanic powers,
principalities,
along with...

1:09:27.899 --> 1:09:30.735
(PRIESTS CONTINUE
READING INDISTINCTLY)

1:09:30.770 --> 1:09:33.375
...air, water, fire...

1:09:36.314 --> 1:09:37.313
Turn around.

1:09:38.415 --> 1:09:39.414
Right now.

1:09:42.914 --> 1:09:43.946
FATHER DANTE:
Raymond, move.

1:09:44.916 --> 1:09:46.421
Are you insane?

1:09:46.456 --> 1:09:48.588
She killed
your sister.
She did not.

1:09:49.294 --> 1:09:51.019
Move.

1:09:51.054 --> 1:09:53.362
NATALIE: Don't act
like a stranger.

1:09:58.028 --> 1:10:00.534
You've got my invitation.

1:10:03.968 --> 1:10:05.000
Natalie.

1:10:06.069 --> 1:10:07.409
Let them leave.

1:10:11.547 --> 1:10:12.546
Natalie.

1:10:20.391 --> 1:10:21.423
(LIGHTS CRACKLE)

1:10:21.458 --> 1:10:23.623
(ALL GASP)

1:10:23.658 --> 1:10:25.856
(METAL CLANGS, CLATTERS)

1:10:26.958 --> 1:10:27.957
(METAL CREAKS)

1:10:30.533 --> 1:10:31.796
Ann.

1:10:31.831 --> 1:10:33.600
(NATALIE HUMMING
ANN'S MOTHER'S SONG)

1:10:34.801 --> 1:10:35.800
(SHUDDERING)

1:10:36.737 --> 1:10:37.802
Natalie.

1:10:39.542 --> 1:10:40.541
Natalie.

1:10:41.841 --> 1:10:46.283
NATALIE:
<i> ♪ I can't hear you ♪</i>

1:10:47.451 --> 1:10:48.615
(DEMONIC SNARL)

1:10:48.650 --> 1:10:49.649
(PRIEST GRUNTS)

1:10:50.949 --> 1:10:52.454
(YELPS, GRUNTS)

1:10:54.590 --> 1:10:57.525
(ALL SHUDDERING)

1:10:57.560 --> 1:10:59.857
(GASPS, SCREAMS)
(ANN WHIMPERS)

1:11:00.893 --> 1:11:01.892
(SCREAM FADES)

1:11:02.532 --> 1:11:03.531
Raymond.

1:11:04.765 --> 1:11:05.764
(DEMONIC SNARLING)

1:11:07.504 --> 1:11:08.503
(WHIMPERS)

1:11:12.377 --> 1:11:13.508
FATHER DANTE:
Raymond!

1:11:21.452 --> 1:11:22.451
Raymond.

1:11:28.459 --> 1:11:29.458
(DEMONIC SNARLING)

1:11:33.123 --> 1:11:34.331
(CHAIN RATTLES)

1:11:35.400 --> 1:11:36.795
(GASPING)
No.

1:11:40.834 --> 1:11:42.834
(UNEASY MUSIC PLAYING)

1:12:12.602 --> 1:12:14.503
(BOTH BREATHING SHAKILY)

1:12:24.548 --> 1:12:26.416
Why did you
leave me, Mommy?

1:12:27.914 --> 1:12:30.552
I was so scared
and alone
without you.

1:12:32.215 --> 1:12:33.687
You're not Natalie.

1:12:33.722 --> 1:12:35.590
I know who I'm talking to.

1:12:42.863 --> 1:12:44.060
(FATHER DANTE
WHISPERING PRAYER)

1:12:44.095 --> 1:12:45.897
Then be honest
for once.

1:12:47.197 --> 1:12:49.098
Why did you
give her away?

1:12:51.069 --> 1:12:53.036
I was 15.
No.

1:12:53.973 --> 1:12:55.071
That's not it.

1:12:57.174 --> 1:12:59.108
What happened
to your mother?

1:13:07.756 --> 1:13:11.428
She sacrificed herself
to save you.

1:13:13.058 --> 1:13:16.730
That's why
you couldn't be
a mother.

1:13:16.765 --> 1:13:19.832
You couldn't
be responsible
for another life.

1:13:23.002 --> 1:13:24.507
But I can now.

1:13:29.173 --> 1:13:30.744
Ann. Ann!

1:13:37.247 --> 1:13:38.455
You win.

1:13:53.538 --> 1:13:55.637
I love you
so much, Mommy.

1:13:55.672 --> 1:13:57.166
(DEMON SNARLS)
(GROANING)

1:14:00.710 --> 1:14:02.710
(TENSE MUSIC PLAYING)

1:14:07.310 --> 1:14:08.947
(PANTING) Natalie.

1:14:16.990 --> 1:14:18.253
Ann!

1:14:18.288 --> 1:14:20.497
(DISTORTED WHEEZING
AND GROANING)

1:14:25.966 --> 1:14:26.998
Run.

1:14:27.033 --> 1:14:29.033
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

1:14:36.141 --> 1:14:37.140
(BONES CRACKING)

1:14:44.347 --> 1:14:45.555
(GROANS IN AGONY)

1:14:49.286 --> 1:14:50.285
(GROANING)

1:14:51.662 --> 1:14:52.661
(FATHER DANTE PANTING)

1:14:55.633 --> 1:14:56.632
(DEMONIC SNARL)

1:15:00.968 --> 1:15:01.967
(DISTORTED GROANING)

1:15:06.138 --> 1:15:07.874
NATALIE:
What's happening?

1:15:07.909 --> 1:15:10.008
Natalie.
I'm Father Dante.

1:15:10.043 --> 1:15:12.879
We're gonna play a game
of hide-and-seek. Okay?
I need you to go through here.

1:15:12.914 --> 1:15:13.913
Come on.

1:15:14.619 --> 1:15:15.618
(WHEEZES)

1:15:16.148 --> 1:15:17.147
(GROWLS)

1:15:18.623 --> 1:15:20.348
Okay. Listen to me.

1:15:20.383 --> 1:15:23.923
I need you to find
the very best hiding spot
that you can, okay? Go.

1:15:23.958 --> 1:15:24.957
Go.

1:15:32.230 --> 1:15:33.229
(PANTING)

1:15:40.040 --> 1:15:41.039
(FOOTSTEPS THUMPING)

1:15:42.141 --> 1:15:43.140
(FOOTSTEPS RUNNING)

1:15:50.721 --> 1:15:52.182
(FOOTSTEPS STOP)
Come on.

1:15:52.217 --> 1:15:53.381
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

1:15:53.416 --> 1:15:54.624
Come on.

1:16:02.931 --> 1:16:04.260
Ann.

1:16:04.295 --> 1:16:05.294
(CHAIN RATTLES)

1:16:07.232 --> 1:16:08.231
(GRUNTS)

1:16:09.201 --> 1:16:10.200
(GASPS)

1:16:15.042 --> 1:16:16.976
Ann, I know
you're in there,
okay?

1:16:17.011 --> 1:16:18.373
I need you
to listen to me,
okay?

1:16:18.408 --> 1:16:20.650
Just let
Natalie go, please?

1:16:20.685 --> 1:16:22.080
Let her go.

1:16:22.115 --> 1:16:23.114
(GRUNTS)

1:16:25.283 --> 1:16:26.282
(BONES CRACKING)

1:16:28.352 --> 1:16:29.351
(HISSES)

1:16:31.927 --> 1:16:32.926
(SLOW FOOTSTEPS)

1:16:37.097 --> 1:16:38.096
(BREATHING SHAKILY)

1:16:44.203 --> 1:16:46.203
(SOFT FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

1:16:56.886 --> 1:16:57.885
(SCREAMS)

1:17:00.153 --> 1:17:01.152
(NATALIE GRUNTING)

1:17:04.223 --> 1:17:06.157
(IN DEMONIC VOICE)
Don't be scared.

1:17:12.198 --> 1:17:13.428
ANN'S MOTHER:
(WHISPERING)<i> Annie.</i>

1:17:16.301 --> 1:17:17.773
<i> Annie.</i>

1:17:22.846 --> 1:17:24.373
<i> Let go, Annie.</i>

1:17:24.408 --> 1:17:26.375
<i> Let go, Annie.</i>
(WHIMPERS)

1:17:27.312 --> 1:17:29.114
<i> Annie, let go.</i>

1:17:29.149 --> 1:17:30.786
<i> Annie, let go.</i>

1:17:32.152 --> 1:17:35.120
<i> I'm here with you.</i>

1:17:35.155 --> 1:17:38.255
ANN:<i> My mother</i>
<i>never stopped fighting</i>
<i>the demon from within.</i>

1:17:39.225 --> 1:17:40.422
Right until the end.

1:17:43.834 --> 1:17:44.833
(GRUNTING)

1:17:50.467 --> 1:17:52.104
(BABY FUSSES)

1:17:52.139 --> 1:17:53.270
(CRIES)

1:17:54.911 --> 1:17:56.438
ANN'S MOTHER:
(WHISPERING)<i> Let go.</i>

1:17:57.243 --> 1:17:58.242
(GASPING)

1:17:59.509 --> 1:18:00.717
(SOBS)

1:18:04.481 --> 1:18:05.480
(GRUNTS)

1:18:07.253 --> 1:18:10.023
(WHIMPERS, GROANS)
<i>I'm here with you.</i>
(ECHOES)

1:18:11.488 --> 1:18:12.487
(GRUNTING)

1:18:13.424 --> 1:18:14.423
(ROARS)

1:18:19.199 --> 1:18:20.198
(STRAINED ROAR)

1:18:23.841 --> 1:18:26.776
(BONE CRACKS)
(SHRIEKS, GROANS)

1:18:26.811 --> 1:18:27.810
Ann!

1:18:29.572 --> 1:18:30.780
(ANN CONTINUES GROANING)

1:18:32.047 --> 1:18:33.046
(GRUNTING)

1:18:35.050 --> 1:18:36.984
Blessed Michael
the Archangel. (GRUNTING)

1:18:38.889 --> 1:18:39.888
(WINCES)

1:18:40.517 --> 1:18:42.055
(SOBBING)

1:18:43.355 --> 1:18:45.553
(DEMONIC GROWL)

1:18:45.588 --> 1:18:47.192
Defend us
in this hour of conflict.

1:18:48.558 --> 1:18:50.063
(STRAINING)

1:18:54.399 --> 1:18:55.398
(ROARS)

1:18:56.533 --> 1:18:57.906
Be our safeguard.

1:18:58.568 --> 1:19:00.469
(STRAINING)

1:19:00.504 --> 1:19:02.009
Thrust Satan
down to hell.

1:19:02.044 --> 1:19:03.307
(STRAINING)

1:19:03.342 --> 1:19:06.013
(DEMONIC ROAR)
(FLESH SIZZLING)

1:19:07.280 --> 1:19:08.950
(GROANING)
(BONES CRACKING)

1:19:08.985 --> 1:19:09.984
(ANN SCREAMING)

1:19:12.153 --> 1:19:13.152
(DEMONIC ROAR)

1:19:17.587 --> 1:19:19.796
(HEART POUNDING)

1:19:21.525 --> 1:19:24.031
FATHER QUINN:
<i> Your power</i>
<i> is in the spirit.</i>

1:19:24.066 --> 1:19:25.098
Not the flesh.

1:19:26.200 --> 1:19:28.233
(HEARTBEAT SLOWING)

1:19:28.268 --> 1:19:30.367
DR. PETERS:
<i> You're on</i>
<i> a new path.</i>

1:19:30.402 --> 1:19:31.500
Keep going.

1:19:33.075 --> 1:19:35.273
You don't have to
hide from it anymore.

1:19:35.308 --> 1:19:36.846
<i>All of the pain.</i>

1:19:39.983 --> 1:19:41.510
ANN'S MOTHER: (WHISPERING)
<i> Let go, Annie.</i>

1:19:50.961 --> 1:19:52.961
(WATER SIZZLING)
(DEMONIC ROAR)

1:19:55.130 --> 1:19:56.129
(ROARING STOPS)

1:20:05.239 --> 1:20:06.238
(LIGHTS CRACKLE)

1:20:07.109 --> 1:20:08.108
Ann.

1:20:09.342 --> 1:20:10.341
Ann.

1:20:13.951 --> 1:20:14.950
Ann.

1:20:17.185 --> 1:20:18.250
(GURGLING, COUGHING)

1:20:20.353 --> 1:20:21.352
(SPITS)

1:20:22.355 --> 1:20:23.926
(GASPS, COUGHING)

1:20:26.029 --> 1:20:28.557
(CONTINUES COUGHING)
(FATHER DANTE PATTING)

1:20:28.592 --> 1:20:29.591
(PANTING)

1:20:41.275 --> 1:20:43.275
(BELL TOLLING)

1:20:50.449 --> 1:20:52.449
(CLICKS BUTTON)
(BED WHIRRS)

1:20:58.622 --> 1:21:01.161
(SOFT MUSIC PLAYING)

1:21:02.296 --> 1:21:03.394
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)

1:21:07.169 --> 1:21:09.202
If you follow me,
we can finish up
the paperwork.

1:21:09.237 --> 1:21:10.236
Of course.

1:21:16.607 --> 1:21:17.606
Hi.

1:21:21.150 --> 1:21:24.118
I know it doesn't
seem like it now,

1:21:24.153 --> 1:21:26.021
but when
you are home

1:21:26.056 --> 1:21:28.958
with your family
and your friends,

1:21:28.993 --> 1:21:30.553
you'll forget
all about this place.

1:21:33.030 --> 1:21:35.294
But I don't want
to forget about you.

1:21:37.298 --> 1:21:39.100
Then don't.

1:21:39.135 --> 1:21:40.134
(CHUCKLES)

1:21:58.154 --> 1:21:59.252
Your train.

1:22:01.718 --> 1:22:03.718
I will treasure this.

1:22:05.227 --> 1:22:06.292
Thank you.

1:22:20.407 --> 1:22:22.176
(SOBBING SOFTLY)

1:22:22.211 --> 1:22:24.211
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATION)

1:22:45.531 --> 1:22:50.138
Without your intercession,
the enemy would've won
this battle.

1:22:50.173 --> 1:22:55.341
You clearly have
an important role to play
in the Church, Sister Ann.

1:22:55.376 --> 1:22:58.410
CARDINAL MATTHEWS:
We've discussed where your
talents might be best placed.

1:22:58.445 --> 1:23:04.119
So, we are rewarding you
an academic research fellowship
at the Vatican.

1:23:06.783 --> 1:23:09.454
A fellowship
in exorcism.

1:23:10.721 --> 1:23:12.721
(GENTLE MUSIC PLAYING)

1:23:16.265 --> 1:23:18.100
Thank you.
(CHUCKLES)

1:23:19.235 --> 1:23:21.367
It's an
unprecedented honor.

1:23:23.371 --> 1:23:25.734
FATHER QUINN:
We think you could make
a difference there, Sister.

1:23:57.900 --> 1:24:00.505
Thank you...
for everything.

1:24:03.444 --> 1:24:04.443
Mmm.

1:24:07.910 --> 1:24:09.349
You know,
technically speaking,

1:24:09.384 --> 1:24:11.450
you're not the first
female exorcist.

1:24:13.619 --> 1:24:16.224
St. Catherine
of Siena?
(CHUCKLES)

1:24:17.359 --> 1:24:18.688
Indeed.

1:24:18.723 --> 1:24:20.525
She died in 1380.

1:24:21.528 --> 1:24:23.330
Right.

1:24:23.365 --> 1:24:26.135
So the first
in seven centuries.

1:24:28.667 --> 1:24:29.765
I'll take it.

1:24:36.609 --> 1:24:39.544
If I may give you
one last
word of advice?

1:24:40.943 --> 1:24:42.415
Of course, Father.

1:24:46.388 --> 1:24:47.519
FATHER QUINN:
<i> Be careful.</i>

1:24:48.753 --> 1:24:50.390
<i> Now that</i>
<i> you know the Devil,</i>

1:24:52.361 --> 1:24:53.492
the Devil knows you.

1:24:55.430 --> 1:24:57.430
(ANN'S MOTHER'S SONG PLAYING)

1:25:07.607 --> 1:25:09.706
WEATHERMAN ON RADIO:
<i>The overnight low</i>
<i>near 47th.</i>

1:25:09.741 --> 1:25:12.379
<i>Rain tapering off</i>
<i>tomorrow afternoon</i>
<i>followed by...</i>

1:25:12.414 --> 1:25:13.413
(CAR HORNS HONKING)

1:25:14.779 --> 1:25:16.680
<i>As for your weather today,</i>

1:25:16.715 --> 1:25:19.188
<i>with the winds</i>
<i>out of the southeast</i>
<i>at 12 miles per hour,</i>

1:25:19.223 --> 1:25:21.289
<i>it's currently</i>
<i>58 degrees.</i>

1:25:38.902 --> 1:25:40.902
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

1:25:51.618 --> 1:25:52.617
DRIVER: (WHISPERS)
Annie.

1:26:01.430 --> 1:26:02.792
Annie.

1:26:02.827 --> 1:26:03.826
(LOCK CLICKS)

1:26:05.929 --> 1:26:07.731
(SHUDDERING)

1:26:07.766 --> 1:26:09.766
(EERIE MUSIC PLAYING)

1:26:27.456 --> 1:26:28.455
(ROARS)

1:26:32.725 --> 1:26:34.725
(DRAMATIC DARK MUSIC PLAYING)
